			<description>内積の定義より、 \begin{eqnarray} \left(\sum_i \lambda_i |w_i\rangle, |v\rangle\right) &amp;amp;=&amp;amp; \left(|v\rangle, \sum_i \lambda_i |w_i\rangle\right)^{\ast} \\\ &amp;amp;=&amp;amp; \left(\sum_i \lambda_i (|v\rangle, |w_i\rangle)\right)^{\ast} \\\ &amp;amp;=&amp;amp; \sum_i \lambda_i^{\ast} (|v\rangle, |w_i\rangle)^{\ast} \\\ &amp;amp;=&amp;amp; \sum_i \lambda_i^{\ast} (|w_i\rangle, |v\rangle) \end{eqnarray}</description>
